.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, tennis, skiing, basketball, volleyball
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, orchid, marigold, tulip
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people have 5 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, magic-tricks, filmmaking, rock-climbing

1. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's sport is weightlifting
2. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's hobby is puzzles
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is tennis
4. the person who growsorchid is the person drinking tea
5. the person who's sport is tennis is to the right of the person who's sport is skiing
6. the old-gold-smoker is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing
7. the kools-smoker is the person who's sport is basketball
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the person who growstulip is the parliaments-smoker
14. the person who growsmarigold is to the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball

.:: Answer ::.
