| Flower	|   marigold	|    orchid	|     daffodil	|    bellflower	|    tulip	|
| Sport		|    basketball	|      volleyball	|      weightlifting	|     skiing	|     tennis	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
